Little to no travel is expected for this position.


SUPERVISION:

None


EDUCATION AND REQUIRED CREDENTIALS:

Bachelor's Degree; Advanced Degree preferred or an equivalent combination of education and experience
Certified Payroll Professional is a plus

EXPERIENCE AND SKILLS:

3- 5 years of experience in a large organization (5,000 employees or more).
Payroll experience with minimum of 3 years processing payroll in Workday system.
Excellent communication, organization, customer service, interpersonal and analytical skills required with the ability to work effectively with third parties. Must be a team player, dedicated, and reliable.
Good time management skills are required. Must be able to execute multiple activities simultaneously.
Experience in a high volume, high intensity position is required with the ability to meet critical processing deadlines under tight time constraints.
Kronos operations experience highly desired.

